2.2 Cleaning Cylinder Capacity¶

From the previous exploration, we found out some data entry errors where some cars which are not electric have cylinder_capacity as Zero, so we'll drop these rows. Also we realized the "Unclassified" section in in the model, so we can explore it further. Also there are a lot of old dates in first use, this will be explored further

In [ ]:
# Drop rows with Cyclinder 0 and not EL cars
df = df.loc[~((df['cylinder_capacity'] == 0) & (df['fuel_type'] != 'EL'))]
len(df)
